{"tid":256570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"低胸露背！唐詩詠容光煥發　避談洪永城","createTime":"2017-05-24T15:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T20:28:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b09ebbe57fbcfb2ca5873c40675bb71a7699aa16","tid":256570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170524/photo/bkn-20170524183719988-0524_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170524214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170524183719988-0524_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170524214819&h=ac39ac60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝員唐詩詠以白色低V露背裙於中環出席品牌活動，講到她失戀後密密賺，詩詠表示：「之前接落嘅。（洪永城有搵你？）呢啲唔評論。（佢話仲愛你？）呢啲唔講喇。（唔係應該更開心？）自己睇咗報導，但冇睇到內容只睇到標題。（話送車送股份畀你？）雜誌講嘅嘢唔評論，我知佢係有睇車，但冇聽過亦冇收。」<br />\n<br />\n問到二人是否沒有翻撻機會？詩詠說：「唔係佢直接講嘅嘢，只係雜誌寫嘅故事唔評論。（佢話你女友光環畀佢壓力？仲話仲愛你？）我收到嘅、佢所講嘅愛係朋友嘅愛。（可以昇華番？）唔講，太遙遠。」問到男方似乎有意箍煲，但詩詠是否已死心？詩詠都不願多講：「之前已經喺網上講咗，唔想一一咁講清楚，以後係點，要經過時間。（唔關第三者事？）已經喺網上講咗原因。（邊個決定分手？）係雙方去傾。」<br />\n<br />\n講到洪永城表現得好傷心，詩詠說：「你又點知我冇傷心呢？感情事想留番畀自己，唔想講，係因為需要時間去處理，唔代表係冇流過眼淚，咁講對我係唔公平，唔代表我冇努力過，將來嘅嘢發生咩都未知，呢個世界咩都有可能。（依家係同事定朋友？）朋友。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170524/bkn-20170524183719988-0524_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170524%2Fbkn-20170524183719988-0524_00862_001.html&d=HruW1db70zuOHVo3azk41gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=cd3d3ddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170524/bkn-20170524183719988-0524_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"605611a9a63e1431bccf5cb7785c1a26d1687801","tid":256570,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559f20a355a7c889c896402666f554e454ef9927","tid":256570,"uid":49487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"#thebestisyettocome<br />\n#活得比你好"},{"pid":"0cdccc3547069f24d1a1ed61c3b302ed692cb100","tid":256570,"uid":14135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"我諗冇男人接受到自己女朋友有契哥"},{"pid":"273bef37f03ab7b8767d3a8a2c836683a41935cc","tid":256570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b3393ea41947404252ced6a6fcde9661e58b97","tid":256570,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:32:11.000Z","msg":"有得見報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe65e312eccd6f7878120948985feb0899a2aca","tid":256570,"uid":4979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650d2e3ac2fba69e702ab84b15016d6af9323c02","tid":256570,"uid":40265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T20:06:37.000Z","msg":"煩撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f5364928bc33ed2ccb817d588ac3ecc883ba7a","tid":256570,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T20:28:30.000Z","msg":"臭雞 扮睇化咗扮心死跟住話重新出發咁"}]}